UDP Client:
    For use:
    udp_client <host> [<port> <number_of_packets>]
    Example:
    client_udp myhost.ru 33333 1000
    client_udp myhost.ru
    client_udp myhost.ru 12345

UDP Server:
    For use:
    server_udp [<port>]
    Example:
    server_udp 33333
    server_udp

Build platform:
*Fedora release 14 (Laughlin)
*Linux kernel 2.6.32-042test005.1.x86_64
*gcc version 4.5.1 20100924 (Red Hat 4.5.1-4) (GCC)
